===Adjective===
'''pedestrian'''

# Of or intended for pedestrians.
#:'''''pedestrian''' crossing''
# Ordinary, [[dull]]; [[everyday]]; [[unexceptional]].
#:''His manner of dress was '''pedestrian''' but tidy.''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# Somebody [[walking]] rather than using a vehicle; somebody travelling on [[foot]].

